: absolute;left: 57px;top: -9.66193px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-6iis64gv fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Unwind in the cozy ambiance of Classique Martini Bar in the heart of Saigon as you sip on our signature Autumn-inspired concoctions. Indulge in the White Russian: a timeless classic made with vodka, Kahlua, and a rich touch of cream. Each sip offers a smooth blend of bold flavors and velvety texture, perfect for the season.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">For a truly glamorous experience, try our Milky Way cocktail &mdash; a luxurious mix that&rsquo;s sweet, nutty, and elegantly crafted with brandy, Frangelico, and cr&egrave;me. Embrace the warmth and indulgence of fall with this celestial creation!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Signature Martini Cocktails are proposed from VND 300,000 ++ per glass<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Daily, 18:00 &ndash; 22:00<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6l7qh5q6 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-3 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-6l7qhibn ffg-empty-space fg-text-dark\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6l7qhcmi fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-6l7qi1th buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Martini-cocktails-web.pdf\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">MENU<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6s38ahrt fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-3 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-6s38ahru ffg-empty-space fg-text-dark\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-47ll6iof{ padding-top: 20px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 50px;}@media (min-width:768px) { .ffb-id-47ll6iof{ padding-top: 20px;padding-bottom: 10px;}}@media (min-w